snippet.title: Antioch: Scarlet Bay - Trailer
snippet.description:
Antioch: Scarlet Bay is an online cooperative narrative adventure.
Play as two detectives working together to solve a murder in the shadowy city of Antioch. 
Wander in a city filled with characters with their own agendas and attitudes, all your decisions change the story and lead to multi endings.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1919140/Antioch_Scarlet_Bay/

Trailer Hand Drawn and Animated by Xavier Sailliol and Jade Crapart
Music : Alex Burnett
